{"id":596629,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/【cdtv】王怡：一旦掌权者公开焚烧圣经-那教会就要/","date":"2018-09-30T03:23:42Z","modified":"2018-09-30T03:24:21Z","title":"【CDTV】王怡：一旦掌权者公开焚烧圣经 那教会就要复兴了","content":"<p><iframe width=\"467\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ww4hZKq4bvc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>2018年9月21日晚，在成都秋雨圣约教会的火炼·为中国教会奋兴赞美会中，王怡牧师说：“我接下来关心的，不是受逼迫或者被抓坐牢，而是正当在受逼迫时期，神将要兴起多少人归主，多少人全职传道服侍主。”王怡牧师在会上呼召献身全职服侍的全职传道人，有34人走上讲台跪下祷告，愿主继续坚固和使用秋雨圣约教会。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1%ef%bc%9a%e4%bb%96%e9%80%bc%e8%bf%ab%e4%b8%bb%e8%80%b6%e7%a8%a3%e5%9f%ba%e7%9d%a3%e7%9a%84%e6%95%99%e4%bc%9a-%e8%8b%a5%e4%b8%8d%e6%82%94%e6%94%b9%e5%bf%85/\">【CDTV】王怡：他逼迫主耶稣基督的教会 若不悔改必要灭亡</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/08/%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1%e7%89%a7%e5%b8%88%ef%bc%9a%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e6%84%bf%e6%84%8f%e9%a2%84%e5%a4%87%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1-%e4%bb%98%e5%87%ba%e4%bb%bb%e4%bd%95%e4%bb%a3%e4%bb%b7/\">王怡牧师：我们愿意预备自己 付出任何代价</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/09/%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1-%e6%88%91%e5%af%b9%e6%96%b0%e3%80%8a%e5%ae%97%e6%95%99%e4%ba%8b%e5%8a%a1%e6%9d%a1%e4%be%8b%e3%80%8b%e7%9a%84%e4%ba%94%e4%b8%aa%e7%ab%8b%e5%9c%ba/\">王怡牧师：我对新《宗教事务条例》的五个立场</a></p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269],"tags":[36295,36293,36292,9791,16428,36294,15207,26149]}